  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, 2nd level, and every 4 levels thereafter, a monk may select a bonus feat. These feats must be taken from the following list:</p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.elephant-in-the-room-feat-taxes.yZLJ85c9AuUWNNSs]{Catch Off-Guard (EitR)}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.h9nHYLxXvIXBTmup]{Combat Reflexes}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.ACEQfonKVqh0fwkK]{Deflect Arrows}, @Compendium[world.elephant-in-the-room-feat-taxes.z7YX1uI4MrNyv0PF]{Dodge (EitR)}, and @Compendium[world.elephant-in-the-room-feat-taxes.Tm6l01PPM6xYWgmO]{Scorpion Stance (EitR)}.</p>\n<p>At 6th level, the following feats are added to the list:</p>\n<p>@Compendium[world.elephant-in-the-room-feat-taxes.vOy4Ey89I5sipW8r]{Deft Maneuvers (EitR)}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.nhUawPP4jfED3CYV]{Gorgon's Fist}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.hc7CRKHvhmKRzNKb]{Greater Grapple}, and @Compendium[world.elephant-in-the-room-feat-taxes.NBAxOZmGdCKAWYZL]{Powerful Maneuvers (EitR)}.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, the following feats are added to the list:</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf1.feats.TbOPtIL8Fv8obXtP]{Improved Critical}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.sOCyCmNxe2MBbEaI]{Medusa's Wrath}, @Compendium[pf1.feats.bHcqTC4Lf3aVl3VO]{Snatch Arrows}, and @Compendium[pf1.feats.ugQyUpqPBDsqLyra]{Spring Attack}.</p>\n<p>A monk need not have any of the prerequisites normally required for these feats to select them.</p>",
